1
00:00:00,140 --> 00:00:03,059
=The Crow Princess of Fortune=

2
00:00:03,060 --> 00:00:04,999
=Episode 14=

3
00:00:04,999 --> 00:00:08,219
My mother just won't give up.

4
00:00:08,220 --> 00:00:11,460
Now she's even resorted
to hurting herself for sympathy.

5
00:00:11,860 --> 00:00:13,340
You're right, Your Highness.

6
00:00:13,700 --> 00:00:17,380
But this time, Consort Shu
brought His Majesty into it.

7
00:00:17,900 --> 00:00:20,100
If you don't go,

8
00:00:20,380 --> 00:00:22,740
it may not look appropriate.

9
00:00:23,340 --> 00:00:24,700
We'll deal with whatever comes.

10
00:00:25,180 --> 00:00:28,740
I also want to see
what she's really after.

11
00:00:29,780 --> 00:00:31,780
But the one I care about most now

12
00:00:32,340 --> 00:00:34,140
is Suisui.

13
00:00:35,100 --> 00:00:37,700
As for that mother son bond,

14
00:00:38,540 --> 00:00:42,279
she can save it for Xiao Jing.

15
00:00:42,280 --> 00:00:45,080
(Imperial Garden)

16
00:00:45,900 --> 00:00:47,379
Does the Crown Prince know

17
00:00:47,380 --> 00:00:49,019
about what I've done?

18
00:00:49,020 --> 00:00:51,660
Your Highness, the Crown Prince
doesn't know a thing.

19
00:00:52,060 --> 00:00:53,980
Good.

20
00:00:54,300 --> 00:00:56,780
The less he knows, the safer he is.

21
00:00:57,900 --> 00:00:59,700
I've already ordered people

22
00:00:59,780 --> 00:01:01,420
to scatter Day Wither Powder

23
00:01:01,500 --> 00:01:03,220
all over this garden.

24
00:01:03,340 --> 00:01:04,459
Once the timing is right,

25
00:01:04,460 --> 00:01:06,419
the moment
the Little Princess opens her mouth,

26
00:01:06,420 --> 00:01:08,980
every flower here will wither at once.

27
00:01:09,580 --> 00:01:13,259
Doesn't His Majesty
refuse to believe she's a jinx?

28
00:01:13,260 --> 00:01:15,860
Then let him see it for himself.

29
00:01:17,340 --> 00:01:19,620
Where are the flowers?
Where are my flowers?

30
00:01:19,860 --> 00:01:22,220
They were still here last night.

31
00:01:26,140 --> 00:01:30,660
Consort Shu,
are you looking for these flowers?

32
00:01:33,420 --> 00:01:36,520
Reporting to Your Highness,  they've all
been pulled out. Not a single one left.

33
00:01:36,520 --> 00:01:38,940
Good. Return now.

34
00:01:42,220 --> 00:01:44,660
How dare you pull out
all the flowers in the Imperial Garden!

35
00:01:44,940 --> 00:01:47,979
The gift prepared for Father was made up
of rare flowers from across the land.

36
00:01:47,980 --> 00:01:50,060
Now that new flowers
have entered the palace,

37
00:01:50,340 --> 00:01:53,060
the old ones naturally had to make room.

38
00:01:54,380 --> 00:01:55,819
Mother.

39
00:01:55,820 --> 00:01:57,660
(Young Xiao Heng)
Why do you want to send me away

40
00:01:57,820 --> 00:02:00,180
just because you have another son?

41
00:02:01,460 --> 00:02:03,299
This palace is so large.

42
00:02:03,300 --> 00:02:07,579
Is there really no place for me here?

43
00:02:07,580 --> 00:02:09,260
Your younger brother is still little,

44
00:02:09,300 --> 00:02:11,180
and you're already fighting
with him over this?

45
00:02:11,780 --> 00:02:13,420
You're so insensible.

46
00:02:14,060 --> 00:02:16,660
Looks like I raised you for nothing.

47
00:02:16,700 --> 00:02:18,300
Throw him out.

48
00:02:22,780 --> 00:02:24,699
Wasn't that exactly

49
00:02:24,700 --> 00:02:27,900
what you taught me back then, Mother?

50
00:02:29,140 --> 00:02:31,179
Are you mocking me?

51
00:02:31,180 --> 00:02:34,059
Oh my, you're his mother.

52
00:02:34,060 --> 00:02:37,339
How can you not understand your own son?

53
00:02:37,340 --> 00:02:39,459
My father wasn't mocking you indirectly.

54
00:02:39,460 --> 00:02:42,259
He was mocking you to your face.

55
00:02:42,260 --> 00:02:43,419
I may not be educated,

56
00:02:43,420 --> 00:02:44,859
then you're uneducated too?

57
00:02:44,860 --> 00:02:45,940
You...

58
00:02:51,980 --> 00:02:53,659
Your Majesty.

59
00:02:53,660 --> 00:02:55,579
Look at how Prince Jing
has raised this child.

60
00:02:55,580 --> 00:02:56,859
This little girl has...

61
00:02:56,860 --> 00:02:58,300
There we go.

62
00:03:03,380 --> 00:03:04,219
Suisui.

63
00:03:04,220 --> 00:03:06,099
The yin yang hotpot
you asked for is ready.

64
00:03:06,100 --> 00:03:07,940
Come eat.

65
00:03:12,500 --> 00:03:14,499
The Bronze Cauldron of the Nation?

66
00:03:14,500 --> 00:03:16,819
(The legendary artifact
used to refine immortal pills.)

67
00:03:16,820 --> 00:03:17,939
(Could it be...)

68
00:03:17,940 --> 00:03:19,139
Hotpot comes first.

69
00:03:19,140 --> 00:03:20,540
Everything else comes later.

70
00:03:20,820 --> 00:03:24,820
Your Majesty,
this is a sacred ancestral relic.

71
00:03:25,980 --> 00:03:27,539
A sacred ancestral relic

72
00:03:27,540 --> 00:03:30,140
should naturally
be used by future generations.

73
00:03:31,100 --> 00:03:32,339
Suisui, hurry and eat.

74
00:03:32,340 --> 00:03:33,740
It'll get cold soon.

75
00:03:34,820 --> 00:03:36,339
How could this happen?

76
00:03:36,340 --> 00:03:38,180
How could this be?

77
00:03:40,180 --> 00:03:40,809
Mother.

78
00:03:40,810 --> 00:03:41,599
Father.

79
00:03:41,600 --> 00:03:43,459
What's happening to the flowers?

80
00:03:43,460 --> 00:03:44,899
Run.

81
00:03:44,900 --> 00:03:45,780
Ah?

82
00:03:50,180 --> 00:03:50,979
Your Majesty!

83
00:03:50,980 --> 00:03:52,459
(Zhu Lingtai)
Your Majesty!

84
00:03:52,460 --> 00:03:54,219
(Imperial Observatory of Tianxuan Kingdom)
Last night, I observed the stars.

85
00:03:54,220 --> 00:03:57,419
An evil star is clashing with the Purple Star.
Now all the flowers have withered.

86
00:03:57,420 --> 00:03:59,660
This is a sign of great misfortune.

87
00:03:59,980 --> 00:04:02,660
An evil force must be at work.

88
00:04:04,500 --> 00:04:06,500
Your Highness?

89
00:04:06,820 --> 00:04:08,140
Why is it you?

90
00:04:08,660 --> 00:04:09,139
Ah?

91
00:04:09,140 --> 00:04:11,020
Who else were you expecting,

92
00:04:11,260 --> 00:04:12,620
Zhu Lingtai?

93
00:04:20,600 --> 00:04:23,919
♪Little lucky star,
twinkling with a wink at me♪

94
00:04:23,920 --> 00:04:27,759
♪Every Chinese New Year day brings
the luckiest fortune slip♪

95
00:04:27,760 --> 00:04:31,279
♪The God of Wealth favors me,
the Matchmaker ties red strings for me♪

96
00:04:31,280 --> 00:04:34,240
♪With firecrackers going off,
good things keep coming one after another♪

97
00:04:35,120 --> 00:04:38,759
♪Make a wish on the very first day
of the Chinese New Year♪

98
00:04:38,760 --> 00:04:42,520
♪By the second day,
my belly's already round♪

99
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:45,919
♪Always talking about dieting,
but the chub never disappears♪

100
00:04:45,920 --> 00:04:49,960
♪Good food brings joy
and happiness every single day♪

101
00:04:55,560 --> 00:04:59,239
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
every year is filled with joy♪

102
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:02,879
♪I'm bringing blessings to everyone♪

103
00:05:02,880 --> 00:05:06,599
♪Hands clasped together in greeting♪

104
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:10,239
♪May every family be sweet and happy♪

105
00:05:10,240 --> 00:05:13,919
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
may everything go your way♪

106
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:15,839
♪Endlessly flowing♪

107
00:05:15,840 --> 00:05:22,040
♪Good fortune♪
